{
  "stem": "6130.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As matter of fact, in one of the pictures you can even see a little trace of geraniums behind the window.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he had a flower bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had a flower bed, a bigger one and some little ones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In that flower bed, the night before we were transported, we tried to same some jewelry, which we all had to give in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this good bracelet I had, was given to me back my youngest brother when I was 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we-- I was hiding that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My niece and I we worked all night long hiding things and hiding things in the cellar, like good fat, and papers, and pictures, my-- my-- my matriculation paper which I have, and whatever, some jewelry, some of my mother's silver, flatware, sterling silver, which has the initials engraved, VJV.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I have some spoons from that I saved and two big ladles, one big, one small.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One was [NON-ENGLISH] one was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That I have.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, otherwise, we gave in everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were told if you don't, you may be transported.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Radio we had to give into the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And because we all had maids-- which it wasn't a big thing in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because it was-- maids came in from the villages, where they were very poor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they had their shelter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they had all the food and a little money, which they saved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they went back to the villages and got married, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very cheap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody had a maid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't show any big richness to have a maid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So these things that you hid in the garden--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we had-- we-- we hid in the flower bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really not the-- a garden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a flower bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
